{"tid":1436503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭琴日已經證明自己言而無信","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:09:30.000Z","uid":232190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8779edbc7010cbea89c46d736162eb6cfb198fe","tid":1436503,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"根本條柒婆話停咗衝擊就會回應訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月8日乜衝擊都冇<br />\n8月8日乜衝擊都冇<br />\n8月8日乜衝擊都冇<br />\n8月8日乜衝擊都冇<br />\n8月8日乜衝擊都冇</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後佢今日回應埋d咁嘅垃圾？<br />\n五大訴求 乜都唔做 仲想打民生牌去打壓示威<br />\n<br />\n到時停咗衝擊 佢大可以話<span style=\"color: gold;\">仲未確定真係停咗</span><br />\n又或者話<span style=\"color: blue;\">民生問題係第一要處理嘅事</span><br />\n<br />\n大家要條柒婆回應訴求先係因為佢言而無信<br />\n所以唔好信佢停咗示威先 佢要遊花園 遊到2047都有得佢遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17593c2406422cfc51355429f96d73e8f5431b9","tid":1436503,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}